headline: 3 Services Stocks We Keep Off Our Radar
summary: Business services providers use their specialized expertise to help enterprises streamline operations and cut costs. Furthermore, the demand for their offerings is rising as more clients outsource non-core functions, a trend that has enabled the industry to return 33% over the past six months. At the same time, the S&P 500 was up 29.3%.
